Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:37.16,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}不断寻找  幸存的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:41.08,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}就算最终无人倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:47.55,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}这也是我最真诚的光之祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:53.18,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}我才明白直面自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:57.01,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}就能变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.77,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}不要放过这每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.60,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}在迷茫与彷徨中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:05.86,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}不断战胜无数个日夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:10.15,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}在这幸存的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.91,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}等待崭新耀眼的开幕式来临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:18.45,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}我们一起去迎接
